0that%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20unsuspecting%20investors%2C%20Musk%20instead%20bought%20more%20than%20%24500%20million%20of%20Twitter%20shares%20at%20artificially%20low%20prices%20before%20finally%20revealing%20his%20purchases%20on%20April%204%2C%202022%2C%20by%20which%20time%20he%20owned%20a%209.2%25%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwitter's%20share%20price%20rose%20more%20than%2027%25%20following%20that%20disclosure%2C%20the%20SEC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20lawsuit%20seeks%20to%20force%20Musk%20to%20pay%20a%20civil%20fine%20and%20disgorge%20profits%20he%20didn't%20deserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20eventually%20purchased%20Twitter%20for%20%2444%20billion%20in%20October%202022%2C%20and%20renamed%20it%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlex%20Spiro%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Musk%2C%20in%20an%20email%20called%20the%20SEC%20lawsuit%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20regulator's%20%26quot%3Bmulti-year%20campaign%20of%20harassment%26quot%3B%20against%20his%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20action%20is%20an%20admission%20by%20the%20SEC%20that%20they%20cannot%20bring%20an%20actual%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Musk%20has%20done%20nothing%20wrong%20and%20everyone%20sees%20this%20sham%20for%20what%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpiro%20added%20that%20the%20lawsuit%20addresses%20a%20mere%20%26quot%3Balleged%20administrative%20failure%20to%20file%20a%20single%20form--an%20offense%20that%2C%20even%20if%20proven%2C%20carries%20a%20nominal%20penalty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOTHER%20LAWSUITS%20OVER%20TWITTER%20PURCHASES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20an%20adviser%20to%20U.S.%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20is%20worth%20%24417%20billion%20according%20to%20Forbes%20magazine%2C%20through%20businesses%20such%20as%20the%20electric%20car%20maker%20Tesla%20and%20rocket%20company%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20worth%20nearly%20twice%20as%20much%20as%20Amazon.com%20founder%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20th