ladesh%20prime%20minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20niece%20Tulip%20Siddiq%20tendered%20her%20resignation%20amid%20growing%20calls%2C%20in%20a%20set%20back%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Ms%20Siddiq%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20family%20connections%20are%20a%20matter%20of%20public%20record%2C%20and%20when%20I%20became%20a%20Minister%20I%20provided%20the%20full%20details%20of%20my%20relationships%20and%20private%20interests%20to%20the%20Government.%20After%20extensive%20consultation%20with%20officials%2C%20I%20was%20advised%20to%20state%20in%20my%20declaration%20of%20interest%20that%20my%20aunt%20is%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bangladesh%20and%20to%20recuse%20myself%20from%20matters%20relating%20to%20Bangladesh%20to%20avoid%20any%20perception%20of%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20I%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20that%20I%20acted%20and%20have%20continued%20to%20act%20with%20full%20transparency%20and%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20officials%20on%20these%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20emphasised%20her%20loyalty%20to%20the%20Labour%20government%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20its%20agenda%20of%20%26quot%3Bnational%20renewal%20and%20transformation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAn%20independent%20review%20has%20confirmed%20that%20I%20have%20not%20breached%20the%20Ministerial%20Code%20and%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20I%20have%20acted%20improperly.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNonetheless%2C%20to%20avoid%20distraction%20for%20the%20Government%2C%20I%20have%20resigned%20as%20City%20Minister.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHere%20is%20my%20full%20letter%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkZeWZfEsei%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FkZeWZfEsei%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Tulip%20Siddiq%20(%40TulipSiddiq)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTulipSiddiq%2Fstatus%2F1879200958359716213%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2014%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20departure%20came%20after%20Bangladesh%20interim%20government%20head%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20condemned%20the%20use%20of%20properties%20gifted%20to%20her%20and%20her%20family%20by%20the%20regime%20under%20Ms%20Hasina.%20Further%2C%20serious%20concerns%20were%20raised%20about%20Ms%20Siddiq's%20links%20to%20a%20graft%20case.%20This%20comes%20amid%20an%20ongoing%20embezzlement%20investigation%20against%20the%20previous%20regime%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20as%20per%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh's%20Anti-Corruption%20Commission%20latest%20investigation%20is%20into%20an%20alleged%20land%20grab%20of%20lucrative%20plots%20in%20a%20suburb%20of%20the%20capital%20Dhaka.%20Earlier%2C%20Hasina%2C%20Siddiq%20and%20other%20family%20members%20were%20targets%20of%20the%20commission's%20investigation%20into%20accusations%20of%20embezzlement%20of%20%245%20billion%20connected%20to%20a%20Russian-funded%20nuclear%20power%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Sunday%20Times%20investigation%20also%20revealed%20that%20Ms%20Siddiq%20spent%20years%20living%20in%20a%20London%20flat%20bought%20by%20an%20offshore%20company%20connected%20to%20two%20Bangladeshi%20businessmen.%20The%20flat%20was%20eventually%20transferred%20as%20a%20gift%20to%20a%20Bangladeshi%20lawyer%20with%20links%20to%20Hasina%2C%20her%20family%20and%20her%20ousted%20government%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%20It%20also%20reported%20Siddiq%20and%20her%20family%20were%20given%20or%20used%20several%20other%20London%20properties%20bought%20by%20members%20or%20associates%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20such%20allegations%2C%20calls%20for%20Ms%20Siddiq's%20resignation%20gained%20momentum.%20Conservative%20leader%20Kemi%20Badenoch%20accusing%20Starmer%20of%20appointing%20%26quot%3Bhis%20personal%20friend%20as%20anti-corruption%20minister%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Baccused%20herself%20of%20corruption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%2C%20however%2C%20after%20fleeing%20Bangladesh%20in%20August%20following%20a%20student-led%20uprising%2C%20has%20been%20living%20in%20India.%20She%20has%20defied%20extradition%20requests%20to%20face%20Bangladeshi%20charges%2C%20including%20of%20mass%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736914020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Frqdl8pr8_tulip-siddiq-twitter_625x300_15_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-minister-tulip-siddiq-resigns-after-bangladeshs-concerns-on-sheikh-hasina-link-7476344%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UK%20minister%20and%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20niece%20Tulip%20Siddiq%20resigned%20as%20the%20anti-corruption%20minister%2C%20in%20a%20setback%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-minister-tulip-siddiq-resigns-after-bangladeshs-concerns-on-sheikh-hasina-link-7476344%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20To%20Visit%20Pakistan%20Ahead%20Of%20Champions%20Trophy.%20Report%20Explains%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlthough%20India%20will%20play%20its%20Champions%20Trophy%20matches%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20the%20team%20captain%20is%20expected%20to%20visit%20the%20host%20nation%20Pakistan%20to%20attend%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20prestigious%20event%2C%20which%20is%20making%20a%20return%20after%20an%20eight-year%20hiatus%2C%20sources%20said.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20is%20planning%20a%20grand%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20tentatively%20scheduled%20for%20February%2016%20or%2017%2C%20subject%20warm-up%20match%20itinerary.%20All%20team%20captains%20are%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20opening%20ceremony%2C%20which%