leged%20and%20disabled%20individuals%20to%20stitch%20the%20bags%20efficiently.%20This%20training%20was%20crucial%20in%20ensuring%20that%20the%20bags%20were%20made%20with%20the%20right%20skills%20and%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECommunity%20impact%20of%20Threads4Good%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThreads4Good%20has%20had%20a%20lasting%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20underprivileged%20women%20and%20disabled%20individuals%20who%20work%20with%20the%20organisation.%20Beyond%20teaching%20them%20to%20stitch%2C%20the%20team%20has%20organised%20various%20sessions%20to%20equip%20them%20with%20valuable%20life%20skills%20like%20learning%20English%2C%20financial%20literacy%2C%20and%20personal%20hygiene%20practices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-18.48.28-1-1-1736084016-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Threads4Good%20has%20upcycled%20more%20than%203%2C600%20kg%20of%20textile%20waste%20to%20make%20bags%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-18.48.28-1-1-1736084016-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-18.48.28-1-1-1736084016-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-18.48.28-1-1-1736084016-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl