lains%20the%20young%20founder%2C%20while%20discussing%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20underprivileged%20students%2C%20like%20Naisha%20Mungilwar%2C%20the%20bags%20were%20more%20than%20just%20an%20aid%20for%20school%20supplies.%20They%20represented%20hope.%20A%20student%20from%20Prashant%20Vidyalaya%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20she%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20where%20survival%20is%20a%20constant%20struggle.%20Her%20father%20works%20as%20a%20labourer%20and%20her%20mother%20is%20a%20maid%20who%20barely%20manages%20to%20feed%20Naisha%20and%20her%20younger%20brother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20school%20on%20most%20days%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20receiving%20the%20bag%20from%20Threads4Good%2C%20I%20started%20attending%20school%20regularly.%20I%20can%20carry%20my%20books%20safely%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371220%2Fias-jitendra-jorwal-transforms-lives-of-underprivileged-children-women-in-rural-punjab-through-education-health-projects%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emid-day%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20organised%20by%20the%20team%20helps%20me%20focus%20better%20in%20class.%20Thanks%20to%20this%2C%20I%20passed%20my%20Class%2010%20with%20flying%20colours%20and%20now%20aim%20to%20become%20a%20doctor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20impact%20of%20Threads4Good%20began%20to%20spread%20across%20the%20community%2C%20Tejas%20realised%20how%20far-reaching%20the%20initiative%20could%20be.%20Volunteers%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20India%2C%20and%20even%20beyond%2C%20rallied%20behind%20the%20cause.%20Soon%2C%20the%20project%20expanded%20to%20multiple%20cities%20including%20Nagpur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20Pune%2C%20and%20is%20now%20growing%20in%20Toronto%20as%20well.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20team%20includes%20more%20than%20400%20volunte