%20was%20his%20PA%20sitting%20in%20the%20car%20specified%20for%20national%20selectors%3F%20They%20can't%20even%20discuss%20things%20in%20private%20with%20an%20unknown%20third%20person%20in%20the%20car.%20Why%20was%20he%20allotted%20space%20in%20the%20BCCI's%20hospitality%20box%20in%20Adelaide%3F%26quot%3B%20an%20irritated%20BCCI%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20did%20he%20have%20breakfast%20in%20the%20cordoned%20off%20area%20of%20a%20five-star%20facility%20which%20is%20just%20earmarked%20for%20the%20team%20members%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20drama%20picking%20pace%20with%20every%20passing%20day%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20wrong%20to%20say%20that%20it%20is%20a%20very%20uneasy%20Indian%20dressing%20room%20that%20is%20heading%20into%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20from%20February%2019%20to%20March%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736909400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flcs89iu_gambhir-pc-pti_625x300_11_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-likened-to-greg-chappell-irritated-bcci-official-slams-coachs-personal-aide-shadowing-team-7472493%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20BCCI%20selector%20said%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20shown%20shades%20of%20mercurial%20former%20coach%20Greg%20Chappell%20in%20his%20approach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-likened-to-greg-chappell-irritated-bcci-official-slams-coachs-personal-aide-shadowing-team-7472493%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Small%20businesses%20are%20suffering%2C%20with%20some%20being%20forced%20to%20shutter%20due%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20fires%22%