mpared%20to%20regular%20business%2C%20and%20the%20costs%20accrued%20from%20being%20closed%20stack%20up%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThankfully%20we%20are%20safe%20and%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20able%20to%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20Betsy%20Martinez%2C%20owner%20of%20Fan%20Girl%20Cafe%20in%20West%20Hollywood%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20business%20has%20definitely%20been%20impacted%20by%20the%20situation%20and%20we%20are%20navigating%20it%20the%20best%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartinez%2C%20who%20runs%20Fan%20Girl%20Cafe%20with%20her%20wife%2C%20said%20the%20pair%20lost%20roughly%20%245%2C000%20in%20just%20two%20and%20a%20half%20days%20of%20closures%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20slow%20business%20in%20the%20days%20since.%20As%20a%20new%20restaurant%20in%20its%20first%20year%20of%20operations%2C%20margins%20were%20already%20tight.%20They're%20now%20considering%20debt%20consolidation%20and%20taking%20out%20a%20new%20loan%20and%20have%20contacted%20their%20existing%20lenders%20asking%20for%20extensions%20on%20their%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20business%20owners%20are%20turning%20to%20the%20local%20community%20for%20financial%20support%2C%20but%20such%20funds%20are%20inconsistent%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20largely%20targeted%20toward%20businesses%20that%20have%20been%20destroyed.%20Restaurants%2C%20including%20Fox's%20Restaurant%2C%20The%20Little%20Red%20Hen%20Coffee%20Shop%2C%20and%20The%20Reel%20Inn%2C%20have%20all%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fla-wildfire-pacific-palisades-malibu-celebrities-neighborhood-a-listers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eburned%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%C2%A0have%20started%20GoFundMe%20campaigns%20to%20raise%20money%20to%20rebuild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartinez%20said%20she%20and%20her%20wife%20aren't%20comfortable%20starting%20a%20GoFundMe%2C%20given%20how%20tight%20funds%20are%20for%20everyone%20else%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that%20other%20businesses%20are%20dealing%20with%20mo