tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-businesses-closing-los-angeles-fires-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Impeached%20South%20Korean%20President%20Yoon%20Arrested%20Over%20Failed%20Martial%20Law%20Bid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korean%20authorities%20on%20Wednesday%20arrested%20impeached%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20over%20insurrection%20accusations%20related%20to%20his%20brief%20declaration%20of%20martial%20law%20on%20December%203%2C%20investigators%20said.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20sitting%20president%20in%20South%20Korea's%20history%20to%20be%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20suspended%20President%20was%20seen%20leaving%20his%20heavily%20fortified%20residence%20in%20central%20Seoul%20in%20a%20convoy%20to%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Corruption%20Investigation%20Office%20(CIO)%20after%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20investigators%20and%20police%20said%20they%20had%20executed%20the%20arrest%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yoon%20had%20been%20holed%20up%20at%20his%20hillside%20residence%20for%20weeks%2C%20behind%20a%20small%20army%20of%20personal%20security%20to%20avoid%20arrest.%20His%20lawyers%20have%20argued%20attempts%20to%20detain%20the%20impeached%20Presidnet%20were%20illegal%20and%20were%20designed%20to%20publicly%20humiliate%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20his%20lawyer%20announced%20that%20the%20president%20had%20agreed%20to%20speak%20to%20investigators%20and%20that%20he%20had%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20residence%20to%20prevent%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20incident%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Yoon%20has%20decided%20to%20personally%20appear%20at%20the%20Corruption%20Investigation%20Office%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Seok%20Dong-hyeon%20said%20on%20Facebook%2C%20adding%20that%20Yoon%20would%20also%20deliver%20a%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%203%2C000%20police%20officers%20and%20anti-corruption%20investigators%20gathered%20at%20his%20residence%20before%20dawn%2C%20pushing%20through%20throngs%20of%20Yoon%20supporters%20and%20members%20of%20his%20ruling%20People%20Power%20Party%20protesting%20attempts%20to%20detain%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20investigators%20announced%20that%20Mr%20Yoon%20had%20been%20arrested.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Joint%20Investigation%20Headquarters%20executed%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20today%20(January%2015)%20at%2010%3A33%20am%20(0130%20GMT)%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20arrest%2C%20Yoon%20can%20be%20held%20for%20up%20to%2048%20hours%20on%20the%20existing%20warrant.%20Investigators%20would%20need%20to%20apply%20for%20another%20arrest%20warrant%20to%20keep%20him%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20their%20second%20effort%20to%20arrest%20Yoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first%20attempt%20on%20January%203%20failed%20after%20a%20tense%20hours-long%20standoff%20with%20members%20of%20Yoon's%20official%20Presidential%20Security%20Service%20(PSS)%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20budge%20when%20investigators%20tried%20to%20execute%20their%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yoon's%20declaration%20of%20martial%20law%20last%20month%20stunned%20South%20Koreans%20and%20plunged%20one%20of%20Asia's%20most%20vibrant%20democracies%20into%20an%20unprecedented%20period%20of%20political%20turmoil.%20Lawmakers%20voted%20to%20impeach%20him%20and%20remove%20him%20from%20duties%20on%20December%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%20is%20deliberating%20over%20whether%20to%20uphold%20that%20impeachment%20and%20permanently%20remove%20him%20from%20office.%20Mr%C2%A0Yoon's%20impeachment%20trial%20began%20Tuesday%20with%20a%20brief%20hearing%20after%20he%20declined%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20his%20failure%20to%20attend%20--%20which%20his%20team%20has%20blamed%20on%20purported%20safety%20concerns%20--%20forced%20a%20procedural%20adjournment%2C%20the%20hearings%20will%20continue%20without%20Yoon%2C%20with%20the%20next%20set%20for%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736908800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F16f8jfb8_yoon-suk-yeol-south-korea-reuters_625x300_06_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-koreas-president-yoon-suk-yeol-arrested-over-failed-martiallawbid-7475945%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22South%20Korean%20authorities%20on%20Wednesday%20arrested%20impeached%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20over%20insurrection%20accusations%20related%20to%20his%20brief%20declaration%20of%20martial%20law%20on%20December%203%2C%20investigators%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-koreas-president-yoon-suk-yeol-arrested-over-failed-martiallawbid-7475945%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%E2%80%99m%20a%20sinner%20like%20everyone%20else'%2C%20says%20Pope%20Francis%20his%20autobiography%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736908113000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117250764%2Cimgsize-871386.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fim-a-sinner-like-everyone-else-pope-francis-says-he-had-a-mischievous-youth%2Farticleshow%2F117250490.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117250490.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20autobiography%2C%20Pope%20Francis%20opens%20up%20about%20his%20%26quot%3Bmischievous%26quot%3B%20childhood%2C%20his%20family's%20immigrant%20history%2C%20and%20his%20surprise%20at%20becoming%20Pope%20in%202013.%20He%20recalls%20his%20Italian%20grandparents'%20journey%20to%20Argentina%20and%20reflects%20on%20his%20own%20growth%2