to%2Fmsid-117250124%2Cimgsize-1180074.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Famaravati%2Fandhra-pradesh-chandrababu-naidu-bats-for-more-children-per-family-model%2Farticleshow%2F117250116.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andhra%20Pradesh%20CM%20Nara%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20has%20once%20again%20underscored%20the%20need%20for%20families%20to%20bear%20more%20children%20to%20counteract%20the%20aging%20population%2C%20warning%20that%20India%20might%20face%20severe%20demographic%20challenges%20if%20current%20family%20planning%20policies%20continue.%20Naidu%20suggests%20policy%20changes%20and%20emphasizes%20proactive%20measures%20to%20leverage%20demographic%20dividends%20by%202047.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SANDEEP%20RAGHAVAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20ITC%20Chairman%20Sanjiv%20Puri%20Said%20About%20L%26amp%3BT%20Chief's%2090-Hour%20Workweek%20Call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWeighing%20in%20on%20the%2090-hour%20workweek%20controversy%2C%20ITC%20Ltd%20Chairman%20Sanjiv%20Puri%20said%20that%20it%20is%20more%20important%20for%20the%20workers%20to%20be%20aligned%20to%20the%20grander%20vision%20of%20the%20company%20rather%20than%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20put%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20analogy%20of%20many%20workers%20building%20a%20castle%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20ask%20a%20mason%20what%20he%20is%20doing%2C%20he%20might%20say%20he%20is%20laying%20a%20brick%2C%20another%20might%20say%20he%20is%20building%20a%20wall%20but%20some%20might%20say%20he%20is%20building%20a%20castle.%20It%20is%20that%20vision%20that%20workers%20should%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20is%20saying%20that%20mean%20if%20he%20would%20rather%20not%20put%20a%20number%20to%20the%20work%20hours%20at%20ITC%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20not%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20rather%20like%20people%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20journey%20(of%20the%20company)%20and%20feel%20passionately%20involved%20and%20kind%20of%20feel%20the%20urge%20amongst%20themselves%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20to%20the%20enterprise.%20That's%20how%20we%20look%20at%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cigarettes-to-consumer%20goods%20conglomerate%20allows%20a%20flexible%20work%20environment%2C%20including%20work%20from%20home%20on%20two%20days%20every%20week%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EITC%2C%20he%20said%2C%20provides%20a%20lot%20of%20flexibility%20in%20working.%20%26quot%3BAlso%20two%20days%20a%20week%2C%20you%20can%20work%20from%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20not%20so%20much%20about%2C%20you%20know%2C%20really%20monitoring%20each%20individual's%20number%20of%20hours.%20It's%20more%20about%20enabling%20individuals%2C%20helping%20them%20to%20actualise%20their%20potential%2C%20and%20then%20reviewing%20what%20goals%20people%20have%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20follow%20a%20controversy%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%2C%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20India's%20largest%20engineering%20and%20construction%20company%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Ltd%2C%20sparked%20on%20social%20media%20when%20he%20said%20employees%20should%20work%2090-hour%20a%20week%20including%20on%20Sundays%20rather%20than%20sit%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20regret%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20make%20you%20work%20on%20Sundays%2C%26quot%3B%20Subrahmanyan%20said%20in%20an%20undated%20video%20of%20his%20discussion%20with%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%20sitting%20at%20home%3F%20How%20long%20can%20you%20stare%20at%20your%20wife%2C%20and%20how%20long%20can%20the%20wife%20stare%20at%20the%20husband.%26quot%3B%20The%20video%2C%20which%20was%20circulated%20widely%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20X%20and%20Linkedin%2C%20led%20to%20heated%20debate%20about%20work-life%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20he%20(Subrahmanyan)%20has%20been%20debated%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20the%20philosophy%20with%20which%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Puri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20explain%20how%20empowering%20the%20employees%20with%20the%20company%20vision%20and%20goal%20was%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVision%2C%20values%20and%20vitality%20are%20what%20ITC%20is%20all%20about%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20in%20making%20sure%20that%20everybody%20understands%20the%20vision%20of%20the%20enterprise.%20We%20use%20a%20part%20of%20the%20vision%20and%20want%20to%20contribute%20to%20making%20the%20vision%20a%20reality.%20And%20we%20enable%20vitality%20by%20our%20processes%2C%20by%20the%20resources%20we%20provide%2C%20by%20the%20freedom%20to%20act%2C%20that%20we%20provide%2C%20the%20empowerment%20that%20we%20provide%2C%20which%20are%20very%20different%20and%20very%20clear%20goals%20for%20individuals%20to%20achieve%2C%20and%20these%20are%20the%20primary%20things%20that%20we%20look%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Subrahmanyan's%20comments%20sparked%20a%20heated%20debate%20about%20work-life%20balance%20in%20the%20country%2C%20a%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20spokesperson%20last%20week%20said%20that%20the%20chairman's%20remarks%20reflect%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Blarger%20ambition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20this%20is%20India's%20decade%2C%20a%20time%20demanding%20collective%20dedication%20and%20effort%20to%20drive%20progress%20and%20realise%20our%20shared%20vision%20of%20becoming%20a%20developed%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20had%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20head's%20views%20drew%20criticism%20from%20some%20peers%20in%20the%20business%20community.%20RPG%20Group%20Chairman%20Harsh%20Goenka%20said%20longer%20working%20hours%20was%20a%20recipe%20for%20burnout%20and%20not%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubrahmanyan's%20comments%20followed%20Infosys%20co-founder%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20suggestion%20of%20a%2070-hour%20workweek%20and%20Adani%20Group%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani's%20%26quot%3Bbiwi%20bhaag%20jayegi%20(wife%20will%20run%20away)%26quot%3B%20remark%20if%20one%20spent%20more%20than%20eight%20hours%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20idea%20of%20work-life%20balance%20should%20not%20be%20imposed%20on%20me%20and%20my%20idea%20shouldn't%20be%20imposed%20on%20you.%20Say%2C%20someone%20spends%20four%20hours%20with%20family%20and%20finds%20joy%20in%20it%2C%20or%20if%20someone%20else%20spends%208%20hours%20and%20enjoys%20it%2C%20that%20is%20their%20work-life%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAath%20ghante%20family%20ke%20saath%20bitayega%20tho%20biwi%20bhaag%20jaayegi%20(Wife%20will%20leave%20if%20one%20spends%20eight%20hours%20with%20family)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work-life%20balance%20debate%20echoes%20a%20similar%20one%20in%20China%20where%20the%20so-called%20996%20culture%20-%20the%20three%20digits%20describe%20a%20punishing%20schedule%20of%209%20am%20to%209%20pm%20six%20days%20a%20week%20-%20is%20being%20debated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736906400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Fbsq3vl6_sanjiv-puri_625x300_13_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fwhat-itc-chairman-sanjiv-puri-said-about-l-t-chiefs-90-hour-workweek-call-7475913%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weighing%20in%20on%20the%2090-hour%20workweek%20controversy%2C%20ITC%20Ltd%20Chairman%20Sanjiv%20Puri%20said%20that%20it%20is%20more%20important%20for%20the%20workers%20to%20be%20