t%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWalmart%20Birkin%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228040aa56-7341-4b99-8d0f-9b5223458541%5C%22%3ESigns%20that%20the%20Wirkin%20is%20an%20obvious%20dupe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20proportions%20of%20the%20Wirkin%20wouldn't%20look%20right%20to%20anyone%20who%20knows%20their%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20and%20knows%20Birkins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20handles%20are%20too%20long%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20crossbody%20strap%20is%20a%20dead%20giveaway%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Birkin%20doesn't%20come%20with%20one.%20To%20my%20knowledge%2C%20the%20only%20Birkin%20with%20a%20strap%20is%20the%20Micro%20Birkin%20if%20you%20exclude%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-iconic-hermes-birkin-handbag-was-invented-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJane%20Birkin's%20first%20Birkin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardware%20is%20also%20almost%20too%20gold%20and%20has%20a%20slightly%20green%20undertone%2C%20which%20a%20real%20Birkin%20wouldn't%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20afar%2C%20the%20imitation%20leather-like%20material%20looks%20almost%20puffy%2C%20which%20also%20throws%20off%20the%20shape.%20I%20can%20also%20tell%20the%20size%20of%20various%20components%20isn't%20of%20regular%20Birkin%20proportions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20I'm%20concerned%2C%20the%20Wirkin's%20design%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20intentionally%20created%20to%20convince%20anyone%20that%20it's%20a%20Birkin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20look%20similar%20%E2%80%94%20but%20major%20changes%20have%20been%20made%20to%20avoid%20confusion%2C%20and%20they%20haven't%20used%20trademarked%20branding%20that%20would%20lead%20someone%20to%20believe%20that%20it's%20a%20real%20Herm%C3%A8s%20Birkin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20likely%20not%20the%20last%20we'll%20see%20of%20Birkin%20dupes%20from%20other%20brands%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20this%20particularly%20iconic%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fbe726c-5d4f-428f-822c-8b2f3db9baf1%5C%22%3EDupes%20are%20fair%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Birkin%20is%20the%20most%20coveted%20handbag%20in%20the%20world%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20surprising%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20dupes%20and%20replicas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReplicas%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftelltale-signs-of-fake-luxury-handbag-from-vintage-luxury-expert-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattempted%20duplicates%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20luxury%20bag%2C%20down%20to%20the%20types%20of%20hardware%2C%20fonts%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDupes%20are%20not%20branded%2C%20like%20the%20bags%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20imitate.%20They%20use%20a%20style%20or%20concept%2C%20alter%20it%2C%20and%20remove%20its%20branding.%20However%2C%20these%20products%20may%20use%20similar%20materials%20and%20have%20similar%20functionalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20approve%20of%20replicas%2C%20but%20I%20can%20get%20behind%20the%20idea%20of%20dupes%20because%20they%20aren't%20made%20to%20trick%20people%20into%20confusing%20them%20with%20the%20real%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20find%20that%20consumers%20I've%20interacted%20with%20have%20become%20more%20conservative%20about%20spending%20on%20luxury%20products.%20Now%2C%20what%20I%20see%20is%20that%20there%20is%20brand%20loyalty%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20among%20consumers%20who%20enjoy%20buying%20products%20from%20specific%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20uptick%20in%20prices%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20dupes%20are%20readily%20available%20could%20drive%20some%20people%20to%20find%20cheaper%20alternatives%20to%20items%20that%20are%20way%20out%20of%20their%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20word%20of%20warning%2C%20though.%20Knowingly%20purchasing%2C%20distributing%2C%20or%20shipping%20inauthentic%20items%20is%20illegal%20under%20federal%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20constitutes%20%26quot%3Btrafficking%20in%20counterfeit%20goods%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20can%20result%20in%20significant%20fines%20and%20potential%20jail%20time%20depending%20on%20the%20severity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-bag-authenticator-walmart-birkin-isnt-real-deal-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736900521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6780a75d8951662c9f1f8a9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-bag-authenticator-walmart-birkin-isnt-real-deal-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Walmart%20is%20not%20trying%20to%20convince%20anybody%20it's%20copying%20the%20real%20deal%2C%20said%20Koyaana%20Redstar%2C%20a%20luxury%20handbag%20authenticator.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-bag-authenticator-walmart-birkin-isnt-real-deal-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TOP%20Hollywood's%20award%20show%20updates%20amid%20LA%20wildfires%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736900462000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117250070%2Cimgsize-51196.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Foscars-to-grammys-top-hollywoods-award-show-updates-post-los-angeles-wildfires%2Farticleshow%2F117249412.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117249412.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHollywood's%20awards%20season%20faces%20significant%20disruptions%20due%20to%20ongoing%20wildfires%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20causing%20delays%20in%20nominations%20and%20events%20for%20major%20awards%20like%20the%20Oscars%2C%20Produce