2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcapitol-flag-lowered-to-honour-jimmy-carter-to-be-raised-for-trump-swearing-in%2Famp_articleshow%2F117249396.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcapitol-flag-lowered-to-honour-jimmy-carter-to-be-raised-for-trump-swearing-in%2Famp_articleshow%2F117249396.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel's%20Air%20Force%20blazes%20air%20superiority%20path%20to%20Iran's%20border%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israel's%20Air%20Force%20now%20dominates%20the%20skies%20right%20up%20to%20Iran's%20border%2C%20thanks%20to%20advanced%20aircraft%20like%20the%20F-35I%20stealth%20fighter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67859a658951662c9f1ff39d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsrael's%20Air%20Force%20now%20dominates%20the%20skies%20right%20up%20to%20Iran's%20border%2C%20thanks%20to%20advanced%20aircraft%20like%20the%20F-35%20stealth%20fighter.%3Cp%3EJACK%20GUEZ%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIsrael%20has%20used%20its%20Air%20Force%20to%20strike%20its%20enemies%20with%20impunity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESyria's%20collapse%20now%20gives%20it%20unprecedented%20power%20in%20the%20air%2C%20right%20up%20to%20Iran's%20border.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20now%20has%20open%20skies%20to%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Middle%20East%20analyst%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20has%20long%20been%20regarded%20as%20the%20Middle%20East's%20premier%20aerial%20fleet%2C%20supplied%20in%20large%20part%20with%20US-made%20aircraft%20and%20munitions.%20But%20in%20the%20past%20year%20it%20has%20gone%20further%2C%20showing%20its%20aircraft%20can%20strike%20any%20of%20its%20adversaries%20with%20impunity%20and%20establishing%20unprecedented%20air%20superiority%20across%20wide%20stretches%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gutted%20Russian%20and%20Iranian-made%20air%20defenses%20in%20Iran%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fits-been-rough-year-for-iran-and-friends-middle-east-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edaring%3C%2Fa%3E%20Iranian%20leaders%20to%20strike%20back%20with%20fewer%20defenses.%20It%20destroyed%20stocks%20of%20Hezbollah's%20missile%20arsenal%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20and%20killed%20its%20top%20leader%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-likely-used-bunker-buster-bombs-strike-kill-hezbollah-chief-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprecision%20airstrike%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20underground%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20power%20was%20so%20formidable%20in%20Syria%20that%20the%20Assad%20regime%20and%20Russia%20secretly%20asked%20Israel%20to%20spare%20Assad's%20military%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewlinesmag.com%2Freportage%2Finside-israels-shadow-war-against-iran-in-syria%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20classified%20documents%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20in%20the%20country%20after%20that%20brutal%20regime%20collapsed%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20that%20collapse%2C%20Israel%20seized%20the%20opportunity.%20The%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20destroyed%20the%20country's%20vast%20majority%20of%20air%20defenses%20and%20Syrian%20military%20stockpiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%2015%20months%20of%20war%2C%20instigated%20by%20the%20Oct.%207%2C%202023%20terrorist%20massacre%20by%20Hamas%20into%20Israel%2C%20the%20IAF%20has%20emerged%20supreme%20and%20is%20basking%20in%20its%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFighter%20pilots%2C%20if%20they%20wanted%2C%20could%20now%20merrily%20fly%20in%20pairs%2C%20with%20visible%20operating%20systems%2C%20at%20any%20altitude%2C%20to%20any%20range%2C%20to%20any%20spot%20in%20Israel's%20first%20circle%20of%20defense%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynetnews.com%2Farticle%2Fbkz8a1chyg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Israeli%20news%20site%20Ynet%20in%20late%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20long%20possessed%20the%20most%20powerful%20air%20force%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20and%20technologically%20advanced%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20boasts%20over%20600%20aircraft%20and%20over%2030%2C000%20active%20personnel%2C%20with%20no%20less%20than%2050%2C000%20in%20reserve.%20It%20operates%20the%20second-largest%20fleet%20of%20F-16s%20in%20the%20world%20and%20is%20the%20only%20regional%20country%20that%20currently%20flies%20the%20F-35%20stealth%20jet.%20Furthermore%2C%20Israel%20has%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnationalinterest.org%2Fblog%2Freboot%2Ff-35i-americas-most-lethal-stealth-fighter-israeli-twist-190417%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eown%20version%20of%20that%20fifth-generation%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20privilege%20no%20other%20country%20enjoys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20overwhelmingly%20consists%20of%20American-made%20aircraft%20that%20also%20include%20Apache%20and%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopters.%20Israel%20also%20flies%20a%20large%20fleet%20of%20F-15s%20and%20recently%20signed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2024%2F11%2Fisrael-signs-5-2-billion-deal-for-25-american-f-15s%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%245.2%20billion%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2025%20highly%20advanced%20F-15IA%20variants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20defense%20of%20Israel.%20It%20gave%20the%20small%20country%20a%20critical%20qualitative%20edge%20over%20its%20larger%20Arab%20adversaries%20in%20historical%20conflicts%2C%20most%20notably%20the%20June%201967%20Six%20Day%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israel's%20Air%20Force%20flies%20numerous%20US-made%20aircraft%20like%20the%20F-15%20Strike%20Eagle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678687f58951662c9f200257%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsrael's%20Air%20Force%20flies%20numerous%20US-made%20aircraft%20like%20the%20F-15E%20Strike%20Eagle.%3Cp%3EJACK%20GUEZ%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF's%20newfound%20supremacy%20goes%20beyond%20previous%20wars.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20previously%20destroyed%20several%20Soviet-built%20Syrian%20surface-to-air%20missile%20batteries%20in%20Lebanon's%20Beqaa%20Valley%20in%20a%20complex%20operation%20in%201982%20and%20shot%20down%20over%2080%20Syrian%20fighter%20jets%20without%20incurring%20any%20losses%20in%20return.%20While%20December's%20operation%20saw%20the%20IAF%20strike%20all%20across%20Syria%2C%20the%20operation%20wasn't%20nearly%20as%20sophisticated%20or%20dangerous%20as%20that%20historical%20episode%3B%20many%20of%20the%20air%20defenses%20in%20the%20latest%20operation%20were%20abandoned%20or%20in%20low%20states%20of%20readiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20one%20reason%20possibly%20restraining%20Israel%20was%20a%20recently%20exposed%20secret%20agreement%20with%20Russia%20and%20Syria%20in%20which%20Israel%20agreed%20to%20refrain%20from%20wider%20targeting%20of%20Syria's%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sebastien%20Roblin%2C%20a%20widely%20published%20military%20aviation%20journalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20launched%20an%20enormous%20long-range%20air%20and%20drone%20attack%20against%20Iran%20on%20the%20night%20of%20October%2026%20in%20retaliation%20for%20an%20Iranian%20missile%20barrage%20against%20it%20on%20October%201.%20The%20IAF%20targeted%20some%20Syrian%20air%20defenses%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20also%20used%20Iraqi%20airspace%20that%20October%20night%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Firan-update-october-26-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20targeted%20early%20warning%20radars%20and%20sensors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20both%20Syria%20and%20Iraq%2C%20which%20were%20part%20of%20a%20network%20Iran%20established%20in%20the%20region%20to%20detect%20incoming%20Israeli%20attacks.%20While%20the%20IAF%20used%20standoff%20munitions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-strike-israeli-air-force-ballistic-missiles-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%20air-launched%20ballistic%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20Israeli%20aircraft%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20penetrated%20Iranian%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20what%20we%20currently%20know%2C%20some%20Israeli%20aircraft%20did%20reportedly%20breach%20Iranian%20airspace%2C%20though%20not%2C%20from%20what%20I've%20seen%2C%20very%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Bohl%2C%20a%20senior%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20analyst%20at%20the%20risk%20intelligence%20company%20RANE%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20in%20part%20a%20demonstration%20of%20capability%20and%20in%20part%20an%20operational%20necessity%20to%20effectively%20hit%20deep%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20stated%20some%20aircraft%20entered%20Iranian%20airspace%2C%20which%20were%20likely%20stealthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-showed-power-of-f-35s-iran-strikes-uk-admiral-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELockheed%20Martin%20F-35%20Lightning%20II%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20newly%20revealed%20long-range%20drones.%20Roblin%20said%20it's%20unclear%20if%20these%20aircraft%20released%20weapons%20over%20Iran.%20They%20could%20have%20been%20there%20to%20help%20%26quot%3Bprecisely%20locate%20key%20targets%26quot%3B%20and%20guide%20weapons%20fired%20by%20other%20aircraft%20over%20significant%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20strike%20certainly%20had%20the%20effect%20of%20dispelling%20deterrence%20benefits%20of%20Iran's%20more%20advanced%20air%20defenses%20(Russian%20S-300%20systems)%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%20However%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20with%20Syria%20before%20December%2C%20Iran's%20remaining%20air%20defenses%20%26quot%3Bstill%20have%20some%20value%20in%20compelling%20use%20of%20more%20expensive%20standoff%20munitions%20and%20perhaps%20absorbing%20a%20percentage%20of%20incoming%20weapons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20campaign%20against%20the%20remnants%20of%20the%20Syrian%20military%20has%20major%20implications%20for%20Iran.%20Should%20Syria's%20airspace%20remain%20permissive%20to%20Israeli%20aircraft%2C%20Israel%20can%20fly%20its%20tanker%20aircraft%20closer%20to%20Iranian%20airspace%20than%20previously%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20medium%2Fhigh-altitude%20air%20defenses%20were%20truly%20fully%20destroyed%2C%20then%20Israel's%20ordinarily%20vulnerable%20tanker%20aircraft%20could%20indeed%20theoretically%20access%20Syrian%20airspace%20and%20refuel%20fighters%2C%20which%20could%20enable%20higher%20volume%20attacks%20on%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Syrian%20air%20defenses%20eliminated%2C%20Bohl%20believes%20that%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20now%20has%20open%20skies%20to%20Iran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20likely%20take%20years%20before%20Syria%20manages%20to%20reestablish%20significant%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one-two-punch%20of%20Assad%20regime's%20collapse%20followed%20by%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20surviving%20equipment%20mean%20Syria%20will%20require%20a%20much%20longer%20time-frame%20to%20reconstitute%20an%20air-%20and%20ground-based%20defense%20capability%20through%20expensive%20new%20equipment%20purchases%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20Israel's%20ability%20to%20attack%20targets%20at%20will%20has%20been%20improved%2C%20though%20it%20was%20already%20more%20than%20adequate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirpower%2C%20of%20course%2C%20has%20its%20limits.%20Israel's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-israel-trying-to-achieve-in-gaza-bombing-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaerial%20bombing%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20damaged%20roughly%20two-thirds%20of%20all%20buildings%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20foot%20patrol%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczj9zzz8xm7o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20and%20killed%20Hamas'%20hardline%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20orchestrated%20the%2010%2F7%20attacks.%20Similarly%2C%20waves%20of%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20have%20failed%20to%20stop%20Iran%20from%20nuclear%20weapons%20development%20and%20uranium%20enrichment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Russia's%20influence%20diminishing%2C%20Turkey%20appears%20destined%20to%20become%20the%20new%20Syria's%20main%20military%20backer.%20Ankara%20has%20already%20offered%20to%20help%20Damascus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturkey-influence-syria-rebuild-military-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erebuild%20the%20Syrian%20military%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20now%2C%20Israel%20can%20ignore%20Syria%20as%20a%20defensive%20layer%20for%20Iran%3B%20it's%20just%20geography%20to%20fly%20over%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20RANE's%20Bohl%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20a%20permanent%20condition%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20Syria's%20air%20defenses%20will%2C%20in%20some%20capacity%2C%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20should%20Turkey%20provide%20them%2C%20(that)%20might%20complicate%20Israel's%20regional%20strategy%20in%20a%20new%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Iddon%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20and%20columnist%20who%20writes%20about%20Middle%20East%20developments%2C%20military%20affairs%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20history.%20His%20articles%20have%20appeared%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20publications%20focused%20on%20the%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%2