er.com%2Finside-youtube-affiliate-marketing-program-challenges-competing-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20Shopping%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20some%20US%20merchants%20are%20exploring%20selling%20goods%20in%20other%20countries%20where%20TikTok%20Shop%20operates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJake%20Bjorseth%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20TikTok%20Shop%20partner%20agency%20Trndsttrs%2C%20described%20the%20flurry%20of%20TikTok%20ban%20planning%20as%20%26quot%3Bdoomsday%20prep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFortunately%2C%20we've%20slotted%20much%20of%20this%20in%20advance%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20quite%20unclear%20where%20brands%20and%20creators%20reliant%20on%20TikTok%20are%20going%20to%20flow%2C%26quot%3B%20Bjorseth%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt'll%20certainly%20be%20a%20turbulent%20few%20months%20for%20folks%20reliant%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20Rechtszaid%2C%20co-CEO%20of%20the%20e-commerce%20agency%20Ghost%20Agency%2C%20said%20the%20company%20has%20similarly%20stopped%20new%20business%20operations%20related%20to%20TikTok%20Shop%20and%20general%20TikTok%20content%20production%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20possible%20TikTok%20shutdown.%20The%20company's%20revenue%20is%20heavily%20tied%20to%20the%20app%2C%20and%20if%20TikTok%20leaves%20the%20US%2C%20Ghost%20may%20need%20to%20consider%20alternative%20paths%20like%20merging%20with%20another%20company%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20our%20existing%20clients%2C%20we've%20aimed%20to%20shift%20them%20to%20alternative%20platforms%2C%20like%20Instagram%20Live%2C%26quot%3B%20Rechtszaid%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it%20is%20challenging%20to%20replicate%20TikTok%20Shop's%20success%20on%20platforms%20that%20do%20not%20have%20the%20combination%20of%20an%20engaging%20algorithm%20and%20native%20shopping%20features.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20Shop%20businesses%20are%20deep%20into%20contingency%20planning%2C%20others%20hope%20to%20extract%20what%20they%20can%20from%20the%20platform%20w