ing%20that%20he%20got%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20all%20anxieties%20were%20laid%20to%20rest%20when%20Foxx%20showed%20up%20to%20see%20a%20rough%20assembly%20of%20some%20scenes%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20100%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Gordon%20said%2C%20recalling%20his%20shock%20when%20Foxx%20strolled%20into%20the%20editing%20bay%20like%20he%20hadn't%20been%20fighting%20for%20his%20life%20mere%20months%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20classic%20Jamie%20style%20he%20was%20smooth%2C%20was%20cracking%20jokes%2C%20holding%20court%2C%20he%20was%20hilarious%2C%20as%20usual%2C%26quot%3B%20Gordon%20said%20of%20their%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGordon%20showed%20Foxx%20the%20thrilling%20plane%20crash%20sequence%20that%20opens%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20got%20really%20excited%20about%20what%20he%20saw%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20star's%20return%20was%20a%20huge%20boost%20for%20production%20morale.%20Then%20word%20came%20that%20filming%20could%20resume%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20doing%20backflips%20and%20just%20hoping%20everything%20would%20remain%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20Gordon%20said.%20%26quot%3BJamie%20went%20through%20a%20pretty%20severe%20thing%2C%20and%20the%20last%20thing%20in%20the%20world%20we%20would%20want%20to%20have%20happen%20is%20the%20stress%20from%20shooting%20to%20cause%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c80fe60-8e1c-4676-aa1f-0048027be823%5C%22%3EGordon%20thinks%20Foxx's%20recovery%20is%20a%20miracle%2C%20and%20on-set%20spontaneity%20led%20to%20even%20better%20scenes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamie%20Foxx%20holding%20a%20gas%20pump%20on%20fire%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6786b9e88951662c9f2029d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22962%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJamie%20Foxx%20in%20%26quot%3BBack%20in%20Action.%26quot%