%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67859a968951662c9f1ff3a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlannel%20refers%20to%20the%20fabric's%20finishing%20process%20that%20gives%20it%20that%20soft%2C%20brushed%2C%20fuzzy%20feeling.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20choosing%20the%20best%20flannel%20sheets%2C%20prioritize%20those%20made%20from%20100%25%20cotton%20or%20cotton%20blends%2C%20which%20will%20feel%20soft%20to%20the%20touch%20while%20maintaining%20breathability.%20Try%20to%20avoid%20synthetic%20materials%20like%20polyester%20or%20nylon%2C%20which%20can%20feel%20less%20luxurious%20and%20trap%20heat%2C%20but%20are%20less%20prone%20to%20wrinkling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrigin%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESets%20made%20in%20Portugal%20are%20particularly%20sought%20after%20due%20in%20part%20to%20the%20long-staple%20cotton%20use%20and%20long-standing%20craftsmanship%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFlannel%20sheets%20are%20measured%20by%20ounces%20or%20grams%20per%20square%20meter%20(GSM)%20to%20evaluate%20warmth.%20A%20higher%20GSM%20means%20thicker%2C%20warmer%20sheets%2C%20perfect%20for%20chilly%20nights.%20In%20our%20guide%2C%20Lands'%20End%20Luxe%20and%20Coyuchi%20Cloud%20Brushed%20Organic%20flannel%20sheets%20weigh%206%20ounces%2C%20making%20them%20the%20densest%20options%20for%20a%20cozy%2C%20toasty%20feel.%20If%20you're%20a%20hot%20sleeper%20or%20prefer%20flannel%20that%20works%20year-round%2C%20consider%20lighter%20options%20like%20The%20Company%20Store%20or%20L.L.%20Bean%20Ultrasoft%20Comfort%20flannel%20sheets%20which%20are%20not%20overly%20thick%20and%20provide%20just%20enough%20weight%20to%20keep%20you%20comfortable%20at%20around%204%20or%205%20ounces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinishing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFlannel%20gets%20its%20fluffy%20texture%20from%20the%20fabric%20being%20brushed%20to%20create%20a%20thick%2C%20fuzzy%20feel%2C%20so%20you'll%20want%20to%20check%20for%20details%20on%20the%20sheets'%20finishing%20process%20to%20find%20the%20softest%2C%20most%20durable%20options.%20For%20example%2C%20Boll%20%26amp%3B%20Branch%20Flannel%20sheets%20add%20a%20brushing%20process%20and%20then%20triple%20shear%20the%20fabric%20to%20reduce%20the%20appearance%20of%20pills.%20Lands'%20End%20brushes%20the%20flannel%20on%20both%20sides%20for%20extra%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224bf85f5d-1d74-42f6-8023-b34dd5619360%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20flannel%20sheets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sheets%20in%20a%20dryer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67859ad0e294a7514e8cdf22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlannel%20sheets%20are%20known%20to%20produce%20lots%20of%20lint%20in%20the%20dryer%2C%20but%20the%20amount%20of%20shed%20should%20decrease%20overtime.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20washed%20and%20dried%20each%20set%20according%20to%20its%20instructions%20at%20least%20three%20times.%20Unless%20otherwise%20indicated%2C%20we%20washed%20the%20sheets%20in%20a%20cold%20cycle%20with%20gentle%20detergent%20and%20dried%20them%20on%20a%20low%20tumble%20cycle.%20We%20also%20noted%20excessive%20lint%20in%20the%20lint%20trap%20and%20any%20pilling%20or%20color%20loss%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20tested%20the%20fitted%20sheets%20on%20a%20king-size%2C%2010-inch%20thick%20mattress%2C%20observing%20any%20slipping%2C%20sliding%2C%20or%20shrinkage%20after%20washing%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20stretchiness%20and%20performance%20of%20the%20elastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20slept%20on%20each%2