%20submarines%2C%20each%20carrying%2016%20nuclear%20missiles%2C%20with%20an%20explosive%20intensity%20roughly%20a%20thousand%20times%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20bombs%20dropped%20on%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20X%20%2F%20%40AComprime%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20X%20%2F%20%40AComprime%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8di8fhvs_ile-longue-nuclear-submarine-base-france-twitter_625x300_14_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20X%20%2F%20%40AComprime%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20four%20nuclear%20submarines%2C%20nicknamed%20'black%20boats'%2C%20at%20least%20one%20of%20them%20has%20always%20been%20on%20patrol%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis%20since%201972.%20According%20to%20the%20doctrine%20they%20follow%2C%20called%20'permanence%20at%20sea'%2C%20their%20role%20is%20to%20disappear%20in%20the%20oceans%20such%20that%20they%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20launch%20a%20nuclear%20attack%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20within%20seconds%20of%20an%20order%20from%20the%20French%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20base%20is%20home%20to%20about%202%2C000%20military%20personnel%20and%20is%20a%20top%20secret%20military%20zone%20in%20France.%20It%20is%20guarded%20like%20a%20fortress%20with%20round-the-clock%20camera%20surveillance%2C%20continuous%20land%20and%20sea%20surveillance%20by%20drones%2C%20biometric%20scanners%20at%20regular%20intervals.%20Mobile%20phones%20are%20prohibited%20in%20the%20area.%20They%20must%20be%20switched%20off%20and%20kept%20in%20signal-proof%20locker%20facilities%2C%20which%20are%20available%20at%20check%20points%20throughout%20the%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20spite%20of%20such%20heavy%20security%20arrangements%2C%20a%20careless%20oversight%20led%20to%20the%20sensitive%20information%20leak.%20The%20reason%20-%20smartwatches%20with%20third-party%20applications%2C%20used%20to%20keep%20health%20and%20fitness%20checks%2C%20could%20pass%20security%20without%20raising%20an%20alarm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20UK's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-14280163%2FCrew-nuclear-submarine-position-Russia-Strava.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaily%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20investigation%20after%20the%20leaks%20revealed%20that%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20more%20than%20450%20Strava%20users%20-%20all%20from%20the%20French%20military%20-%20have%20been%20active%20in%20the%20top%20secret%20nuclear%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20report%20in%20French%20newspaper%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fen%2Fvideos%2Farticle%2F2025%2F01%2F13%2Fstravaleaks-dates-of-french-nuclear-submarine-patrols-revealed-by-careless-crew-members_6737005_108.html%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELe%20Monde%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20journalists%20found%20that%20many%20of%20the%20military%20personnel%20did%20not%20even%20use%20pseudonyms%20or%20aliases%2C%20keeping%20their%20real%20identities%20public%20on%20the%20fitness%20app.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20even%20kept%20their%20profile%20public%20-%20effectively%20being%20visible%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20instances%2C%20an%20officer%20went%20for%20a%20run%20along%20the%20docks%20where%20the%20nuclear%20submarines%20were%20moored.%20This%20was%20in%20January%20and%20February%20of%202023.%20He%20recorded%20these%20runs%20on%2016%20occasions%2C%20on%20different%20dates.%20On%20February%203%2C%202023%20he%20even%20recorded%20his%20timing%20and%20location%20on%20the%20app.%20His%20account%20then%20went%20quiet%20and%20his%20usage%20of%20Strava%20went%20off%20radar%20for%20over%20a%20month.%20His%20activities%20on%20the%20app%20resumed%20again%20on%20March%2025%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20cases%20were%20recorded%20of%20two%20other%20officers%20who%20also%20recorded%20their%20fitness%20details%20on%20Strava%20on%20the%20same%20dates%20as%20the%20officer%20mentioned%20above.%20They%20too%20went%20off%20radar%20between%20February%203%20and%20March%2025%20that%20year.%20This%20made%20it%20amply%20clear%20that%20all%20three%20men%20went%20on%20patrol%20aboard%20a%20nuclear%20submarine%20between%20those%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20embarrassment%2C%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20even%20chatted%20on%20the%20fitness%20app%20upon%20his%20return%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BIt's%20tough%20to%20get%20back%20into%20sport%20after%20more%20than%20two-and-a-half%20months%20in%20a%20poo%20box.%26quot%3B%20He%20posted%20the%20message%20with%20emojis%20of%20bubbles%20and%20a%20scuba%20diving%20mask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Le%20Monde's%20StravaLeaks%20investigation%2C%20bodyguards%20of%20the%20French%2C%20American%2C%20and%20Russian%20Presidents%20also%20use%20the%20Strava%20fitness%20app%2C%20and%20the%20Presidents'%20movements%20and%20trips%20could%20be%20anticipated%20and%20tracked%20through%20the%20bodyguards'%20Strava%20accounts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736877360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ft59iq5ro_nuclear-submarine-generic-pixabay_625x300_14_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstrava-fitness-app-leads-to-massive-security-breach-on-french-nuclear-submarines-7474295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officers%20and%20crew%20aboard%20a%20French%20nuclear%20submarine%20have%20accidentally%20blown%20their%20cover%20as%20well%20as%20their%20location%20and%20schedule%20by%20recording%20their%20runs%20and%20jogs%20on%20a%20fitness%20app.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstrava-fitness-app-leads-to-massive-security-breach-on-fren