ympic%20Committee%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20star%20pistol%20shooter%20Manu%20Bhaker%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20her%20two%20Paris%20Olympics%20bronze%20medals%20replaced%20by%20identical%20models%20as%20she%20is%20among%20the%20large%20group%20of%20athletes%20who%20have%20complained%20that%20their%20medals%20have%20already%20deteriorated.%20A%20lot%20of%20athletes%20from%20across%20the%20world%20have%20also%20posted%20pictures%20of%20their%20worn%20out%20medals%20on%20social%20media%20in%20recent%20times.%20It%20has%20been%20learnt%20that%20the%20colour%20of%20Bhaker's%20medals%20has%20%26quot%3Bcome%20off%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20%26quot%3Bhave%20been%20in%20that%20state%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20long%20while%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamaged%20medals%20will%20be%20systematically%20replaced%20by%20the%20Monnaie%20de%20Paris%20(the%20French%20state%20mint)%20and%20engraved%20in%20an%20identical%20way%20to%20the%20originals%2C%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iron%20pieces%20embedded%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20each%20Olympic%20medal%20weigh%2018%20grams%20(about%20two-thirds%20of%20an%20ounce).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20state%20mint%20is%20a%20state-owned%20company%20that%20mints%20coins%20and%20other%20currency%20for%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20damaged%20and%20defective%20medals%20are%20to%20be%20replaced%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20as%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20organising%20committee%20is%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20Monnaie%20de%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Olympic%20and%20Paralympic%20medals%20in%20Paris%20featured%20pieces%20of%20the%20iconic%20Eiffel%20Tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%205%2C084%20gold%2C%20silver%20and%20bronze%20medals%20for%20Paris%202024%20were%20designed%20by%20luxury%20jewellery%20and%20watch%20firm%20Chaumet%20(part%20of%20the%20LVMH%20conglomerate)%20and%20produced%20by%20the%20Monnaie%20de%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EB