ear!%20And%20it%20comes%20in%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20shades%2C%20like%20a%20whole%20palette%20of%20it.%20Then%20there%20are%20bunny%20tails%2C%20which%20are%20super%20easy%20to%20grow.%20No%20matter%20how%20healthy%20they%20are%2C%20they%20still%20bloom%20beautifully%2C%20and%20drying%20them%20is%20a%20breeze.%20Plus%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20like%20a%20blank%20canvas%20for%20dying%3B%20you%20can%20dye%20them%20in%20almost%20any%20shade%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20are%20some%20flowers%20that%20can%20really%20test%20your%20patience.%20Baby%E2%80%99s%20breath%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20notoriously%20difficult%20to%20grow.%20It%E2%80%99s%20so%20tricky%20that%20we%20have%20to%20resort%20to%20tissue%20culture%20just%20to%20get%20it%20going.%20People%20love%20it%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20high%20demand%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20easiest%20flower%20to%20work%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202407px)%20100vw%2C%202407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.21.20-PM-1_11zon-1735581833.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cheerful%20assembly%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Dianthe%20team%20midst%20packaging%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.21.20-PM-1_11zon-1735581833.jpeg%202407w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.21.20-PM-1_11zon-1735581833-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.21.20-PM-1_11zon-1735581833-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-29-at-9.21.2