rals%20user%20for%20five%20years%2C%20shares%20how%20switching%20to%20organic%20pads%20changed%20her%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20discovering%20Bliss%20pads%20in%202019%2C%20I%20dreaded%20travelling%20during%20my%20period.%20The%20constant%20friction%20and%20fear%20of%20rashes%20always%20held%20me%20back.%20However%2C%20since%20I%20switched%20to%20organic%20options%2C%20my%20periods%20no%20longer%20disrupt%20my%20travel%20plans.%20Now%2C%20I%20can%20travel%20comfortably%20and%20confidently%2C%20just%20like%20any%20other%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20of%20my%20friends%20who%20struggled%20with%20irregular%20periods%20while%20using%20synthetic%20pads%20saw%20their%20cycles%20normalize%20after%20switching%20to%20Bliss%20pads%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20impressive%2080%25%20customer%20retention%20rate%2C%20over%203.5%20lakh%20supporters%2C%20and%20more%20than%203.3%20million%20products%20sold%20between%20April%20and%20November%202024%2C%20Bliss%20Naturals%20is%20making%20a%20significant%20impact%2C%20all%20thanks%20to%20the%20power%20of%20kenaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20back%20sustainably%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAligned%20with%20eight%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%2C%20the%20kenaf%20fibre-based%20pads%20also%20offer%20a%20climate-friendly%20solution.%20Niveda%20highlights%20that%20their%20products%20%E2%80%9Cemit%20143%20times%20less%20carbon%20compared%20to%20traditional%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20contributing%20to%20reduced%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20truly%20test%20their%20sustainability%20claim%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20conduct%20a%20little%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20sha